summary: Dan thanking bbc studios for believing in them during the Mukbang video is so sweet because it feels like he's thanking the bbc...
body: Dan thanking bbc studios for believing in them during the Mukbang video is so sweet because it feels like he’s thanking the bbc for believing in them in regards to more than just the tour/DVD. It feels like he’s thanking them for the radio show. He’s thankful that the bbc believed in him and Phil before they were famous; that they believed in them enough to help them become more famous in the first place.
